# Teachers Gallery Tech Stack (Short Version)

- **Frontend**: Next.js (React, server-side rendering)  
- **Backend**: Supabase (PostgreSQL, Auth, Storage)  
- **Styling**: CSS Modules or Tailwind CSS  
- **Deployment**: Vercel  

